<p>Havesting water is fine and in France the Government actually give you an incentive with agrant if you install a watrer harvestor. However I have learnt here in UK the Water authority actaully own all the wate even that which falls from heaven onto you property. How they are going to police that God only knows<br />
I was going to import water harvestors from Malaysia to UK until I learnt of this UK law. Does anyone know the detals of this edict. Alan from Cornwall, UK</p>
