<p>Sam, Just like you can use a ghost address to obscure your physical address you can also use ghost email addresses. For example, you can setup an anonymous email account for all your newsletter subscriptions and then privately and securely check it using a VPN or TOR and a private browser within a TrueCrypt volume. Another solution is Mailinator.com but they will only keep the emails for about 24 hours.</p>
